short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en_AU,en_GB,e: 用于启用 Web 自动化的加载项。
short.en: Add-on for enabling web automation. This web extension is worked for Naturobot.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Used to provide communication with the Chrome browser. Naturobot enables you to automate manual processes and tasks on your computer.
Install extensions to automate actions such as Web scripting, data extraction, Web testing, Web forms filling, making API calls, and more. It will also enable the Naturobot recorder.
This browser extension requires Naturobot RPA to run properly. Make sure you have downloaded it and will install it to your device.
